{"word":"H5383 - נָשָׁה - nâshâh - naw-shaw' - Creditor","slug":"H5383","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָשָׁה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nâshâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-shaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Creditor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D4; - na&#x0302;sha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>naw-shaw'</i><p/>A primitive root (rather identical with <a href=\"#/H5382\">H5382</a>, in the sense of <a href=\"#/H5378\">H5378</a>); to <i>lend</i> or (by reciprocity) <i>borrow</i> on security or interest: - creditor, exact, extortioner, lend, usurer, lend on (taker of) usury."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4874\">H4874</a>, <a href=\"#/H5386\">H5386</a>"}]}